## Content-Security-Policy (CSP)

Prosjektet har **streng CSP** via django-csp (`settings.py`, `csp.middleware.CSPMiddleware`). Inline script/style må bruke `nonce="{{ request.csp_nonce }}"`; nye domener (CDN, embeds, media, API-kall) krever oppdatering av `CSP_*` i `settings.py`. Se `.cursor/rules/csp.mdc` for konkrete sjekkpunkter.

## Dev environment (Windows)

- Run Django and shell commands from the project venv, not the system Python.
- Venv: `C:\Users\andre\envs\andynor_py313_django512\Scripts`
- Project root: `C:\Users\andre\Documents\GitHub\andynor`
- CMD one-liner to open a shell with venv activated and cwd set to the repo:
  `cmd /k "cd /d C:\Users\andre\envs\andynor_py313_django512\Scripts & activate & cd /d C:\Users\andre\Documents\GitHub\andynor"`